# Agentic AI image specific requirements (UBI9, Python 3.11, CPU-only).
#
# This file declares top-level intent only. Concrete pins (including all
# transitive deps) are resolved by `pip-compile` into
# compiled_base_functional_specific_llm_agentic_agentic-ai.txt and used by
# build.sh when present. Keep this list short and add new top-level deps here
# rather than copying transitive pins from the compiled lockfile.
#
# Resolver-friendliness:
# - The "Spine pins" block below anchors the small set of packages that are
#   shared across many LangChain/LlamaIndex/Google/AWS deps. Without these
#   pins pip's resolver hits ResolutionTooDeepError on large unpinned graphs.
# - Floors keep us on supported APIs; ceilings prevent surprise major bumps.
# - Avoid pinning *transitive* packages here; pip-compile will lock them.

# --- Spine pins (anchor heavy shared deps) ------------------------------------
